text: Edgar Tallado is a Filipino politician from the province of Camarines Norte in the Philippines. He currently serves as a Governor of Camarines Norte. He was first elected as Governor of the province in 2010 and was re-elected in 2013 as his second term, third term in 2016 and last term in 2019. ==Cancellation of certificate of candidacy== In October 2015, Tallado was dismissed by the Ombudsman of the Philippines. ==References== * * * * ==External links== *Province of Camarines Norte Official Website Category:Living people Category:Governors of Camarines Norte Category:PDP–Laban politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
